asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

name: Victor Charlie
description: Hey Fluf, Im Charlie. My friends call me VC. Ive been through a few battles in my time but Ill never stop running no I wont look back. I prefer to spend my time loving these days, enjoying the finer things in life like Mooncrust Pizza and metaverse games and JADU jetpacks. I walked away from the pain and trauma of war missing an eye, but I still have my hope and faith in changing the world for the better. Now Im a full time fluffer and enjoy playing AIFA football and following amazing projects like Altered State Machine and Fluf World. Im addicted to Fluf actually, youre all just so welcoming and I love the community. So thanks for taking me in to your fluffle. Once youre my friend I will always have your back. Roger that?

description:
She's the life of the party,
everywhere she goes,
ready to go all night,
she'll keep you on your toes.

You will find her dancing all night,
to her favourite Fluf track,
just like her black Mullet, 
she's 'business in the front' and 'party in the back'.

With her piercing White Reptile Eyes,
and a Cheetah Fur to match,
her Bunny mum had a threesome
and what a creature did she hatch!

There is no one quite like her
and everybody knew it,
she really is one of a kind,
Miss Jennifur Fluf Hewitt

A Fluf female is a rare breed indeed, and Harriet is one of the spiciest of the bunch! 

Raised in a burrow with brothers, she carved her own path, joining the CIA as a secret agent and spy. Harriet speaks six languages, and is a master of disguise.  In her free time she enjoys practicing circus arts, including clowning (hence the nose) and marching in a whistle and kazoo band. She also loves hoverboard and jet pack races. 

Multi-talented Harriet sparkles in her tube top and is thinking of breeding soon to the right Fluf (s). She’s progressive that way. This honey bunny is ready to rock the world!

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

Welcome to the Fluffle.
